## AI Intake Engine Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[User Inputs] --> B{Asset Type}
    B -->|Images| C[Gemini Vision via image_url]
    B -->|PDFs| D[Gemini file_url]
    B -->|Audio/Video| E[Gemini file_url + transcription]
    B -->|URLs| F[Text extraction]
    B -->|Text/Voice| G[Direct text analysis]
    C & D & E & F & G --> H[processIntakeAssets]
    H --> I{Floor Plan?}
    I -->|Yes| J[analyzeFloorPlan reuse]
    I -->|No| K[Skip]
    J & K --> L[Gemini + outputSchema]
    L --> M[IntakeResult]
    M --> N[suggestedInputs + confidence + reasoning]
```

Key design decisions:
- **Pure function** — no DB imports, no side effects in the engine
- **Reuses [analyzeFloorPlan()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/floor-plan-analyzer.ts#89-198)** for floor plan images/PDFs
- **Validates all enums** against ProjectInputs constraints before returning
- **Per-field confidence** (high/medium/low) with reasoning explanations

